---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Dental Implants in Footscray | Permanent Solutions for Missing Teeth"
  description="Discover the benefits of dental implants at Top Dentists Footscray. Our expert implant services provide a permanent solution for missing teeth, offering a natural look and feel with long-lasting results."
>
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-background">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <nav class="text-sm text-neutral-500 mb-6">
          <ol class="flex items-center space-x-2">
            <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-primary-500 transition-colors">Home</a></li>
            <li>/</li>
            <li><a href="/services" class="hover:text-primary-500 transition-colors">Services</a></li>
            <li>/</li>
            <li class="text-neutral-800 font-medium">Implants</li>
          </ol>
        </nav>
        
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <h1 class="text-h1 font-heading font-bold text-neutral-800">
            Dental Implants
          </h1>
          
          <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
            <p class="text-lg text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
              Dental implants are a long-lasting, natural-looking solution for missing teeth. At Top Dentists Footscray, we work closely with trusted specialists to provide you with the highest quality implant treatment.
            </p>
            
            <p class="text-lg text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
              An implant consists of a titanium post surgically placed into the jawbone, acting as a replacement for the missing tooth root. After healing, a custom-made crown is attached to the implant, restoring both function and aesthetics.
            </p>

            <!-- Implant Process -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg space-y-6 observe-fade">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-6">
                The Implant Process
              </h3>

              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-800 flex items-start space-x-3">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span>Comprehensive evaluation</span>
                </h4>
                <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed ml-9">
                  We conduct a thorough evaluation to determine if you are a suitable candidate for implants. This may include X-rays and 3D imaging to assess your jawbone density and plan the implant placement.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-800 flex items-start space-x-3">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span>Surgical implant placement</span>
                </h4>
                <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed ml-9">
                  The titanium post is placed into your jawbone, which will then be allowed to heal and integrate with the bone over several months.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-800 flex items-start space-x-3">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span>Custom crown fabrication</span>
                </h4>
                <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed ml-9">
                  Once the implant is secure, we take impressions to create your custom crown.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-800 flex items-start space-x-3">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span>Final restoration</span>
                </h4>
                <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed ml-9">
                  The crown is attached to the implant, completing your restoration.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Benefits -->
            <div class="bg-primary-50 rounded-xl p-8 observe-fade">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-4">
                Benefits of Dental Implants
              </h3>
              <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                <div class="space-y-2">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary-700">Permanent Solution</h4>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">Implants can last a lifetime with proper care</p>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-2">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary-700">Natural Feel</h4>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">Functions and feels like your natural teeth</p>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-2">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary-700">Bone Preservation</h4>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">Prevents bone loss in the jaw</p>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-2">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary-700">No Impact on Adjacent Teeth</h4>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">Doesn't affect neighboring healthy teeth</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Care Instructions -->
            <div class="bg-green-50 rounded-xl p-8 observe-fade">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800 mb-4">
                Caring for Your Implants
              </h3>
              <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                Throughout the process, we provide you with detailed instructions on care and maintenance to ensure the long-term success of your implant.
              </p>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
                <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span>Maintain excellent oral hygiene</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span>Regular dental check-ups and cleanings</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span>Avoid smoking and excessive alcohol</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- Success and Timeline -->
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-12">
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800">
                  Implant Success Factors
                </h3>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
                  <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span>Excellent stability and comfort</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span>Confidence when eating and speaking</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span>Natural-looking aesthetic results</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span>Improved overall quality of life</span>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-800">
                  Treatment Timeline
                </h3>
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                  <p class="text-primary-600 font-semibold text-lg mb-2">
                    3-6 months
                  </p>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">
                    Total treatment time for implant integration and crown placement, resulting in your permanent tooth replacement.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Call to Action -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-primary-500 text-white text-center">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 observe-fade">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-8">
        <h2 class="text-h2 font-heading font-semibold">
          Ready for a Permanent Tooth Replacement?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-primary-100">
          Discover if dental implants are right for you. Call
          <a
            href="tel:96875050"
            class="text-white font-semibold hover:text-primary-100 transition-colors"
          >
            9687 5050
          </a>
          for a consultation
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://apac.dentalhub.online/soe/new/%20?pid=AUTOP01"
          class="btn bg-white text-primary-500 hover:bg-primary-50 text-lg inline-block"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          Book now
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>